  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Siege of Darry</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Darry</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> surrender</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/33px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"33\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/66px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br />\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Lannister.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/45px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/60px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/45px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/60px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">Kingdom of the North</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">the Trident</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>:<br />\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\">House Tallhart</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Tallhart.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Tallhart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/20px-House_Tallhart.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/30px-House_Tallhart.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/40px-House_Tallhart.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Entire garrison</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>siege of Darry</b> is a short siege during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Siege\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Siege</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Castle Darry</a> is <a href=\"/index.php/Recapture_of_Darry\" title=\"Recapture of Darry\">recaptured</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Lannister\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lannister\">Lannister</a> occupation by the forces of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">House Darry</a>. However, a fortnight later, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> falls upon the castle and <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Darry\" title=\"Sack of Darry\">puts it to the sword</a>, killing the eight-year-old Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Darry\" title=\"Lyman Darry\">Lyman Darry</a> and extinguishing <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">House Darry</a> in the male line.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Siege\">Siege</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Siege\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a> leads <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\">Tallhart</a> men in a brief siege of Castle Darry that results in the surrender of the Lannister garrison.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Darry is once again free of Lannister occupation. At <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> sends word to Ser Helman to put the castle to the torch and the Lannister captives to the sword in the name of King <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>. Helman is to then join forces with <a href=\"/index.php/Robett_Glover\" title=\"Robett Glover\">Robett Glover</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Duskendale\" title=\"Battle at Duskendale\">attack Duskendale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Following the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> grants Darry to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> At the end of the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>, the Lannisters claim the Darry lands and marry Lancel to <a href=\"/index.php/Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Amerei Frey\">Amerei Frey</a>, the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Mariya_Darry\" title=\"Mariya Darry\">Mariya Darry</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Events#The_War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Events\">War of the Five Kings</a> calculations.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_7\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 7\">Chapter 7</a>, Catelyn I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_65\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 65\">Chapter 65</a>, Sansa VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 64\">Chapter 64</a>, Arya X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"Template:War of the Five Kings\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"Template talk:War of the Five Kings\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">